@YourSenpai You absolute ape lol, we wouldn't even be talking about this if you hadn't disputed my very short comment that wasn't even addressed to anyone. You want me to keep my opinions to myself when you clearly care about them enough to start this discussion. I don't care if I'm "flamed or mocked."
